POS BOM Integration - Advanced Stock Validation
================================================

This Odoo addon integrates Bill of Materials (BOM) functionality with Point of Sale,
providing comprehensive BOM validation and automatic inventory deduction when products
with BOM are sold.

The module is licensed under LGPL-3 to ensure it remains free and open-source while
allowing integration with proprietary Odoo installations.
